ObserverManager:
Observable notification manager which links the notifications to the scene and
stage state.

This class allows for:
- Deferred notifications when scene or stage is inactive.
- Simple [Observer, Observable] cleanup on scene cleanup.

Install:
- Move observer.js, observer-manager.js into application source tree.
- Include observer.js, observer-manager.js via sources.json

Usage:
- Instantiate an ObserverManager object within a scene's setup method.
- Register notification [Observer, Observable] pairs
- Cleanup ObserverManager instance in scene's cleanup method.

Related Files:
- observer-manager-test.js : Automated test of this component.

